    <string name="help_summary">
        Add new threads by sharing a link (e.g. https://boards.4channel.org/5/thread/123456) to ThreadWatch.
        You can use your favorite browser\'s share feature while viewing a thread.
        \n\nLong-press a thread in the list for options to disable, view stats, delete, etc.
        \n\nTap the bell icon to toggle showing notifications.
        ThreadWatch will continue to refresh as long the refresh rate is not \"Never\".
        Swipe down on the list to refresh immediately.
        \n\nLast Page Warning: This will display if a thread will be deleted or archived soon.
        \n\nI\'d just like to interject, but this will always be free and open source software.
    </string>

